By the time I got home and broke open the food I realized both burgers had mayo on it and both drinks (which were suppose to be dr pepper) ended up being nothing more than glorified carbinated water with a slight brown tint. There are honest mistakes and then there is a level of incompetence that makes me question how you managed to make it this far in life. It takes real pro levels of skill to fail this hard. This level of fail is mathematically not an accident, you were bound to accidentally get at least 1 thing right.
